HEADWORD: Peritropal
<hw>Per*it"ro*pal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/, fr.
<?/ to turn around; <grk>peri`</grk> around + <?/ to turn: cf. F.
<ets>p⟦eacute⟧ritrope</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Rotatory;
circuitous.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
